Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這邊倒是絕贊辛苦中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這也是加深羈絆的合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止打哈欠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 也犯不著打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那率直小女孩是演的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真會裝純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫它商務笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從剛才就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種零件在設計圖裡可沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺拿著它更能拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擅自加二設！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 蠢貨們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我覺得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救世界的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 小心音太寵著灰吹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒沒沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.72,ps,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}un deux trois
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 好痛 為啥還要打兩下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一下是心音的份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 大家好好幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真來勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有點小愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直優先藝人活動 所以沒在別人家住過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你家的老媽看著就囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛀蟲！好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說就沒有能一起過夜的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 大家 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起做個 能在慶典上拿一等獎的紙燈籠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了 花嵐 我們回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學生的藝人活動是到20點為止 這不是常識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要合宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到七夕慶典的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是織man和牛郎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是織女還是man 你給我分分清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們兩個 是從很久很久以前就開始交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼長時間一般來說會厭倦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是欠揍的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織女和…牛郎星…都很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織女和牛郎星都是非常漂亮的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以周圍也肯定有許多的星星喜歡著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他們兩個 眼中都只有對方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得周圍的星星都好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們去店裡睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就留在DIGIBACO了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天…那些… 可能…忘在家裡…了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這個時間一個女孩子在外面晃實在太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了 我…我自己…會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴我忘了什麼 我去幫你拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是忘了拿內衣 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我去取來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 我可是救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但感覺這人太沒節操了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽…陽君 不會覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的…說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…時候…不…不是…這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不知道從什麼時候開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我的夢想 是成…為一名女演員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在廣闊的舞台上…面對許…許多的觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這樣…的話 我…我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本…傳達不到任何人…那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那種事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 你的聲音確實地傳達到了我那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快來人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的聲音 帶我來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了可以拯救世界的這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有你的聲音 所以我才會站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽…君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情愉悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我就將你解放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽…君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君 是文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:10.33,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-17\fn方正大标宋_GBK\pos(397,601)}本日臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Outlane連結完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影屏障展開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機體 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿佐谷上空視野良好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未發現民用飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空筱 土聞 兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理以及精神值均在安定範圍內推移
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector引擎量子線圈 突破臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體調整完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀 戀 戀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀~~！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來大幹一場吧 翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲合體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:13:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馳騁吧 AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀 戀 戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間的文字侵蝕率 目前是42%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空筱 土聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先拖住文字怪獸 防止它繼續侵蝕文字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回可沒有救世主man的出場機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可以用武器弱化文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣是無法徹底了結它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後 果然還是要依靠創聲力來對其造成致命一擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要保護好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空筱 土聞 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀 戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你說你喜歡我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑 是你先說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字侵蝕率上升 已經超過了65%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當空間內的文字被完全被侵蝕之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在現實世界中 甚至連其概念都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有Vector準備出擊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻投影出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神？你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:15:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的戀愛…要保護 我必須要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 是受到了文字怪獸的影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出擊 月銀舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定要了結它 努蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要合體了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲合體 吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合體？但是這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是合體了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡ARION
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 夠倒霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在無法操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情…抑制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 要保持清醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是…因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你正在抹殺你的創聲力 抹殺你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要壓制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從心底吶喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的願望說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心音 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我一點都不喜歡你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見嘍 再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見嘍 再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是因為你他才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法正常的說出話是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是壓力造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治療要花費相當的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說 說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真正的心情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷害到他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過AQUARION流淌進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比任何人都相信聲音的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太過相信所以感到了恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音力量 也許會讓他人變得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我差不多點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別激動 土聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失戀光波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…你錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會輸給你的聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你的聲音裡包含了什麼的樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會全部一起承受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 吶喊吧 綺聲神心音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你真正的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君應該是關注著小舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在兩人也正在合體中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…即使這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…也想和陽君合體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一起 又有什麼不可以的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲合體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃耀吧 AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 三人一起也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀戀戀戀戀戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.07,ps,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(645,662)}ANGEL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的合體形式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是三人合成一體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就像織女 牛郎 和花子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花子是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 文字侵蝕率急速的上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要到危險區域了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我的思念解放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射穿它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月陽戀歌！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有管我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你看起來挺結實的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙真是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會向小豬們屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…我們有愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 還算順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 明明文字怪獸都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份悸動卻沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:08.52,post - white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-17\pos(632,431)}發現了一個明明很可愛\N卻稍微有點遺憾的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就是在這附近看到舞亞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防曬霜準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替換的胖次也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小花嵐你要去哪裡玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零食最多只能買300圓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:23:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 零 零食
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,套餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要忘記帶無線 羅盤和夜視鏡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.22,ps,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,675)}Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 第五話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回來！我們的夏天
